  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK407">
<l>nuṇmā ṇuḻaipula millā ṉeḻilnala</l>
<l>maṇmāṇ puṉaipāvai yaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The beauty and goodness of one who is destitute of knowledge by the study of great and exquisite works, is like (the beauty and goodness) of a painted earthen doll.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
